name: Interactive CD Sampler Disc Vol. 11
overview: Interactive CD Sampler Disc Volume 11 is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Various and published by SCEA, which was released in 1999. This contains a variety of playable demos and videos for several games. Included demos on the disc: Ape Escape, Contender, Croc 2, Interplay Sports Baseball 2000, Jade Cocoon: Story of Tamamayu, MLB 2000, The Next Tetris, NFL Xtreme 2, Sesame Street: Elmo’s Letter Adventure, Tony Hawk’s Pro Skateboarding. Videos: NFL Game Day 2000, PlayStation Underground.
